Package: securedrop-app
Source: securedrop-app
Version: 0.2.1
Architecture: amd64
Maintainer: Ubuntu Developers <james@pressfreedomfoundation.org>
Depends: securedrop-app-interfaces,securedrop-app-hardening,securedrop-app-ossec
Section: web
Priority: optional
Homepage: https://pressfreedomfoundation/securedrop
Description: SecureDrop App Server (metapackage depending on the latest version)
 This is a metapackage to install the securedrop-app-interfaces,
 the securedrop-app-hardening and the securedrop-app ossec packges. You will need to
 run /opt/securedrop/post-install.sh to see auth values for ssh and the document
 interface. Without this information you will be locked out of the servers.
